    "title": "Vacancy for Production Engineer at Luminous Power Technologies International Enterprises",
    "description": "Luminous Power Technologies International Enterprises has an exciting opening for a Production Engineer at our Thane office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Luminous Power Technologies International Enterprises:\nLuminous Power Technologies International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Luminous Power Technologies International Enterprises!",
